data.description: Welcome to 4125 Springruff Dr, a cozy property nestled in the heart of Valdosta, GA 31602. This inviting home offers 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms spread and 1293 square feet of living space. It is situated on a .18-acre lot, and has a brand new chain link fence installed in the back yard to keep the kids and furry family members safe and secure. The highlight of this home is its picturesque backyard, as it backs up to a serene pond, offering a very peaceful atmosphere.  The HVAC system was completely replaced over the summer this year, which ensures that you'll stay cool during the hot summers and cozy during the cooler months.  Convenience is key with the u-shaped driveway, providing ample parking space for you and your guests. The location of this home is truly unbeatable, with easy access to I-75 and just a short distance from Moody Air Force Base, making commuting a breeze.  In summary, 4125 Springruff Dr offers a perfect blend of comfort, convenience, and tranquility. Whether you're looking for a peaceful retreat or a place to create lasting memories with loved ones, this home is an ideal choice. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this beautiful property your own!
